  "3245890": {
    "name": "Upstream",
    "steam_appid": 3245890,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>他们的旅程充满了无与伦比的本能、无尽的韧性，以及为了子孙后代而不能失败的雄心。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245890/extras/a4f81a174d1c08160b73188ff9ee6742.poster.avif?t=1742950902\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245890/extras/a4f81a174d1c08160b73188ff9ee6742.webm?t=1742950902\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245890/extras/a4f81a174d1c08160b73188ff9ee6742.mp4?t=1742950902\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这款具有挑战性的基于物理的平台游戏中，只需使用两个按钮，您就可以扮演一条鲑鱼回家！请记住，在穿越无数障碍和不断出现的危险的旅程中，您对逆境的反应决定了您的成功。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245890/extras/a80194fefbc1a398e955d603953b6c43.poster.avif?t=1742950902\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245890/extras/a80194fefbc1a398e955d603953b6c43.webm?t=1742950902\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245890/extras/a80194fefbc1a398e955d603953b6c43.mp4?t=1742950902\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >只需使用左、右按钮，即可像产卵的鲑鱼一样游泳和跳跃到达山泉。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >穿越基于太平洋西北地区不同生态系统的环境。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果您的进步并不总是向前（或向上），请体验有关鲑鱼生命周期的教育性和情感故事，并在途中获得一点鼓励。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过收集鲑鱼浆果和鲑鱼感官并找到所有秘密区域来满足您的完美主义。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >利用诸如“按键重新绑定”、“按住游泳”和“快速保存模式”等辅助功能设置，按照自己的节奏享受游戏乐趣！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一条可爱的鲑鱼。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245890/extras/03b379cf999535febb6432ad37ae79e5.poster.avif?t=1742950902\" width=800 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245890/extras/03b379cf999535febb6432ad37ae79e5.webm?t=1742950902\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245890/extras/207f581ebcc0381fc21a0edf5100f158.poster.avif?t=1742950902\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245890/extras/207f581ebcc0381fc21a0edf5100f158.webm?t=1742950902\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245890/extras/207f581ebcc0381fc21a0edf5100f158.mp4?t=1742950902\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >鲑鱼产卵的现实是危险的，所以即使是最有经验的平台游戏玩家和速通玩家也会面临挑战。在旅途中留意替代路线。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245890/extras/a27b50ee24d208ab9cc093e88a81ce65.apng?t=1742950902\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245890/extras/a27b50ee24d208ab9cc093e88a81ce65.poster.avif?t=1742950902\" class=\"bb_img\" width=600 height=105 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >只有两个按钮的游戏不会那么难吧？</p>",
